graph TD
    A([User message via /chat]) --> B[init: Initialize State]
    B --> C[authenticate: Extract Customer ID]
    
    C -->|Authentication Fails| D[request_auth_info: Request ID/Email]
    C -->|Authenticated| E{Has Order ID?}
    
    E -->|No| F[list_orders: Show Order History]
    E -->|Yes| G[extract: Parse Order ID & Amount]
    
    F --> G
    G --> H[check_policy: Validate Policy via LLM]
    
    H -->|Valid| I[process: Execute Refund Transaction]
    H -->|Invalid| J[generate_response: Generate Final Response]
    
    I --> J
    J --> K([Response Returned to Client])